summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of that portion of Government Lot 3, Section 32-24-4, located at the southwest corner of 5th Avenue South and Cloverdale Street; and Lots 7 to 11 inclusive, Block 3, Star Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding two new sections numbered 2-266 and 17-213, respectively.
